headline: Colgate-Palmolive Webcasts 2025 Fourth Quarter & Full Year Earnings Conference Call January 30, 2026 – 8:30 a.m. ET
summary: NEW YORK, January 16, 2026--Colgate-Palmolive Company (NYSE:CL) will provide a live webcast of its 2025 fourth quarter and full year earnings conference call on Friday, January 30, 2026, at 8:30 a.m. ET. The call will be hosted by Chairman, President and CEO, Noel Wallace, Chief Financial Officer, Stan Sutula, and Chief Investor Relations Officer and EVP, M&A, John Faucher.
